:

1. *Sami* smo izabrali svoj put. (We chose our own path.)
2. *Sami* smo odgovorni za svoje postupke. (We are responsible for our own actions.)
3. *Sami* ćemo rešiti ovaj problem. (We will solve this problem ourselves.)
4. *Samim* sebi smo najbolji savetnici. (We are our own best advisors.)
5. *Samu* sebe moramo da podstičemo. (We must motivate ourselves.)